Package: shokenuse
Type: Package
Title: Visualize LLM Token Usage Across Tools and Machines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Martin", "Frigaard",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "mjfrigaard@pm.me"
  )
Description: Reads and aggregates LLM token usage from Claude Code (JSONL
    project files), with support for manual CSV imports from other sources
    (Anthropic Console, Posit AI assistants). Provides a Shiny dashboard for
    exploring total usage, cost estimates, trends over time, and breakdowns
    by source, project, and model.
